description: An enumeration of how many composite children a job execution has in each state. Only applicable for COMPOSITE_PARENT jobs.

newState.description: The number of children with status NEW

fileUploadedState.description: The number of children with status FILE_UPLOADED

parsingInProgressState.description: The number of children with status PARSING_IN_PROGRESS

parsingFinishedState.description: The number of children with status PARSING_FINISHED

processingInProgressState.description: The number of children with status PROCESSING_IN_PROGRESS

processingFinishedState.description: The number of children with status PROCESSING_FINISHED

commitInProgressState.description: The number of children with status COMMIT_IN_PROGRESS

committedState.description: The number of children with status COMMITTED

errorState.description: The number of children with status ERROR

discardedState.description: The number of children with status DISCARDED

cancelledState.description: The number of children with status CANCELLED
